# Dependencies
The PyStarTrails package needs the following packages:

* [matplotlib](https://matplotlib.org/stable/index.html)
* [NumPy](https://numpy.org/)
* [OpenCV](https://opencv.org/)
* [tqdm](https://tqdm.github.io/)

